<taxonomicName id="5B46854F06B0873699B2C45D64FC1BAD" authority="Ten." class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Melilotus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="null" pageNumber="528" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="neapolitanus">
Melilotus 
<normalizedToken id="586F4F502E1A5148A3C2009F543AC062" originalValue="neapolitánus" pageId="null" pageNumber="528">neapolitanus</normalizedToken>
Ten.
</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="E391905960084770526AF7EACF45D3EA" pageId="null" pageNumber="528" type="vernacular_names">
<paragraph id="5497F332E2147154D59C1B493BE16E1A" pageId="null" pageNumber="528">Neapolitanischer Honigklee</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="7AC58D2C673CE99CB0E8D0E65490DF41" pageId="null" pageNumber="528" type="description">
<paragraph id="65F3A6AF28840C5B930745580862B1FD" pageId="null" pageNumber="528">
1 
<normalizedToken id="C56F5A5646FBC50C32B20E19342335F2" originalValue="jährig" pageId="null" pageNumber="528">jaehrig</normalizedToken>
; 10-40 cm hoch. 
<normalizedToken id="E9956164815C72DBA682402F68B2833B" originalValue="Blütenstand" pageId="null" pageNumber="528">Bluetenstand</normalizedToken>
1-2 cm lang (ohne Stiel), 8-15 
<normalizedToken id="309A9ECC94D03E26DCE73C44D3AE4EAA" originalValue="blütig" pageId="null" pageNumber="528">bluetig</normalizedToken>
. 
<emphasis id="8A273C1E55796668B08797AD28CA171C" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="528">Krone 4-5 mm lang</emphasis>
, gelb; 
<emphasis id="C8BC75FDA8CD04069489382F1B5A2C88" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="528">
Fahne und Schiffchen etwa gleich lang, 
<normalizedToken id="AAF0880410F8F5ABFB90EE709107D186" originalValue="Flügel" pageId="null" pageNumber="528">Fluegel</normalizedToken>
etwas 
<normalizedToken id="E214824165BD35226B84996537AE406D" originalValue="kürzer" pageId="null" pageNumber="528">kuerzer</normalizedToken>
. Frucht meist aufrecht abstehend
</emphasis>
(bei den andern Arten 
<normalizedToken id="DEC93496AC929BEAA756233F91D5AD53" originalValue="hängend" pageId="null" pageNumber="528">haengend</normalizedToken>
), 
<emphasis id="D780C6B8BEF033ED77667689DE47768A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="528">3-5 mm lang</emphasis>
, zuerst zerstreut und kurz anliegend behaart, zur Reifezeit kahl, mit netzartigen Rippen, meist 1samig. - 
<normalizedToken id="500F059E93148D106043E09578B3955E" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="528">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: 
<normalizedToken id="64BFE98688A1348906CD345772670936" originalValue="Später" pageId="null" pageNumber="528">Spaeter</normalizedToken>
<normalizedToken id="3E8259FC0FED573B181967522B88675A" originalValue="Frühling" pageId="null" pageNumber="528">Fruehling</normalizedToken>
und Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="6133BF715FE2CC724A835042A654F204" pageId="null" pageNumber="528">
<emphasis id="F81A845AB3C242CE74CEA58D27539970" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="528">Zytologische Angaben. 2n</emphasis>
= 
<emphasis id="E00A41E9B7290D33C75657C0768E1223" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="528">16:</emphasis>
Material unbekannter Herkunft (Tschechow aus Darlington und Wylie 1955), aus Italien (Larsen 1955).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="F1D3F6C55C2A1A07EA97EA90BF23BB99" pageId="null" pageNumber="528">
<emphasis id="FAE7506F5469F31E259F7D309BD56AFE" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="528">Standort.</emphasis>
Kollin. Trockene, steinige und sandige 
<normalizedToken id="E566C223CB6F4116B62CC8EF586E4DC4" originalValue="Böden" pageId="null" pageNumber="528">Boeden</normalizedToken>
in warmen Lagen. Felsensteppen, Felsen, Alluvionen, Bahnareale.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="CBF4DE66CDC3310733807B6AD10B001E" pageId="null" pageNumber="528">
<emphasis id="19002A98FD6747BF2C3EF7CCA1B7A3BC" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="528">Verbreitung. Mediterrane Pflanze:</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="5C726E3DD1CAA2022ED0B8EE89DF3B55" originalValue="Nordwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="528">Nordwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis 
<normalizedToken id="35E051C5A6625D761323443A0089CFD1" originalValue="Pyrenäen" pageId="null" pageNumber="528">Pyrenaeen</normalizedToken>
, Savoyen, Istrien; 
<normalizedToken id="8CB5FB0D485CEA2CABC5DBBDF758EC29" originalValue="Südwestasien" pageId="null" pageNumber="528">Suedwestasien</normalizedToken>
(
<normalizedToken id="52F837F089315109FBB1E3C3B3C6CD47" originalValue="ostwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="528">ostwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis Persien), Nordafrika. - Im Gebiet: Savoyen (Maurienne), Bergamasker Alpen (Sarnico); sonst selten adventiv.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
